						               													<description>Glonk Le Choc des Aliens is a small print (150 for the moment) game, self-published by a French designer. Rules are in French.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game use the mechanics of the finger pitch to simulate a galactic war, each wood circular pawns representing a flying saucer. The mechanism of controlled pitch is the same developed in Pitch Bowl.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player control an armada and each armada consists of a spacial base and 8 to 12 flying saucers, with different powers :&amp;#10;- The Sinistrum Empire (malice, trickery),&amp;#10;- The United Worlds Organization (defense),&amp;#10;- The Zorgs (brutality),&amp;#10;- The Space Pirates (speed),&amp;#10;- The Little Grey Ones (technology,teleportation),&amp;#10;- The Invaders (number)&amp;#10;Each have their own powers to take the advantage.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to destroy the other and reaching 7 points. You earn 1 point by killing an enemy flying saucer and 1 point for an enemy base.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For this, the flying saucers can project their opponents in the black hole or asteroids, use certain powers, boarding enemy ships or launch heroic assault against them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The official blog ( http://glonk.sosblog.fr/) offer a campaign for two players based upon 1st trilogy of Star Wars : Pitch Wars.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules in English available.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
